		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;The Vision Technology Service is a Regional Assessment Centre for High Technology Vision Aids for the&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.health.gov.on.ca/en/public/programs/adp/about.aspx&quot;&gt; Assistive Devices Program&lt;/a&gt;, a funding program run by the Ontario Ministry of Health and Long-Term Care.&lt;/p&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;The Vision Technology Service is a Regional Assessment Centre for High Technology Vision Aids for the&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.health.gov.on.ca/en/public/programs/adp/about.aspx&quot;&gt; Assistive Devices Program&lt;/a&gt;, a funding program run by the Ontario Ministry of Health and Long-Term Care.&lt;/p&gt;
